== 用途 ==
三氧化二钕可以用来制作涂料[[玻璃|玻璃]]，包括[[太阳眼镜|太阳眼镜]]、制造{{le|固态激光|solid-state laser}}、以及为玻璃和[[搪瓷|搪瓷]]涂色<ref name="inorg">
{{Citation
| last = Eagleson
| first = Mary
| year = 1994
| title = Concise Encyclopedia of Chemistry
| publisher = Springer
| isbn = 978-3-11-011451-5
| pages = 680
| url = https://books.google.com/books?id=Owuv-c9L_IMC&pg=PA680&dq=%22Neodymium(III)+oxide%22
| access-date = 2009-03-18
}}</ref> 一些含钕涂料玻璃吸收黄光和绿光，所以是紫色的，也可以用于[[焊接|焊接]][[护目镜|护目镜]]。<ref name="nate">
{{Citation
| last = Emsley
| first = John 
| year = 2003
| title = Nature's Building Blocks
| publisher = Oxford University Press
| isbn = 978-0-19-850340-8
| pages = 268–9
| url = https://books.google.com/books?id=j-Xu07p3cKwC&pg=PA268&dq=%22Neodymium+oxide%22
| access-date = 2009-03-18
}}</ref> 一些含钕涂料玻璃是{{le|双色性|dichroic}}的，也就是会随着光照而改变颜色。 一种以矿物{{le|alexandrite}}命名的玻璃在阳光下为蓝色，在人造光源下为红色。<ref name="glass">
{{Citation
| last = Bray
| first = Charles
| year = 2001
| title = Dictionary of Glass
| edition = 2
| publisher = University of Pennsylvania Press
| isbn = 978-0-8122-3619-4
| pages = 103
| url = https://books.google.com/books?id=KbZkxDyeG18C&pg=PA102&dq=%22Neodymium+oxide%22
| access-date = 2009-03-18
}}</ref>全世界每年生產約7000噸的'''三氧化二釹'''，可用來染色[[玻璃|玻璃]]和陶瓷材料，製取[[光学玻璃|光学玻璃]]和激光元件。三氧化二钕也可以用做[[聚合反应|聚合反应]]的[[催化剂|催化剂]]。<ref name="nate"/>

